experimentSetting

Class ExperimentSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • experimentSetting.ExperimentSettings

  • public class ExperimentSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    Class encapsulating all experiment settings: algorithm which is run (e.g. co-training or RSSalg), feature splitting algorithm, etc. Singleton object
